## Remarks  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="a88fe-685"><xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader>類別中已過時[!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)]。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a88fe-685">The <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader> class is obsolete in [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)].</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a88fe-686">您可以建立對其進行驗證<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>所使用的執行個體<xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings>類別和<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a88fe-686">You can create a validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> instance by using the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings> class and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Create%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a88fe-687">如需詳細資訊，請參閱 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 參考頁面的＜備註＞一節。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a88fe-687">For more information, see the Remarks section of the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> reference page.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a88fe-688">使用者需要測試傳回的型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a88fe-688">The user needs to test for the returned type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a88fe-689">例如，套用至物件的</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a88fe-689">For example,</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
object obj = vreader.SchemaType;  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaType)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaType st = (XmlSchemaType)obj;  
   // use XmlSchemaType object  
 }  
 if (obj is XmlSchemaDatatype)  
 {  
   XmlSchemaDatatype sd = (XmlSchemaDatatype)obj;  
   Type vt = sd.ValueType;  
   // use XmlSchemaDatatype object  
       }  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a88fe-690">執行 XML 結構描述驗證時，如果`XmlSchemaType`或`XmlSchemaDatatype`對應至目前正在讀取的項目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a88fe-690">If XML Schema validation is being performed, the `XmlSchemaType` or `XmlSchemaDatatype` corresponds to the current element being read.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a88fe-691">如果正在執行文件類型定義 （DTD 驗證），則這個屬性會傳回`null`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a88fe-691">If document type definition (DTD validation) is being performed, this property returns `null`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a88fe-692">`XmlSchemaDatatype` 傳回目前的項目或屬性，如果是簡單類型，可以指定特殊的驗證條件約束上簡單的型別，如 min 和 max。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a88fe-692">`XmlSchemaDatatype` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a simple type that can specify special validation constraints on the simple types, like min and max.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a88fe-693">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` 如果是會傳回目前的項目或屬性，使用者定義的簡單型別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a88fe-693">`XmlSchemaSimpleType` is returned if the current element, or attribute, is a user defined simpleType.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a88fe-694">`XmlSchemaComplexType` 如果是會傳回目前的項目是使用者定義的 complexType。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a88fe-694">`XmlSchemaComplexType` is returned if the current element is a user defined complexType.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a88fe-695">此類型不能傳回屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a88fe-695">This type cannot be returned by attributes.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="a88fe-696">如果<xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A>已設定 ValidationType.None，任何資料類型資訊提供從結構描述或 Dtd。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a88fe-696">If <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.ValidationType%2A> has been set to ValidationType.None, no data type information is provided from either schemas or DTDs.</span></span>  
  
> [!CAUTION]
>  <span data-ttu-id="a88fe-697">在呼叫<xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>，SchemaType 將會傳回 Null。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a88fe-697">After calling <xref:System.Xml.XmlValidatingReader.Close%2A>, SchemaType will return Null.</span></span>  
  
   
  
